  <num>7-2505.01</num>
  <heading>Sales and transfers prohibited.</heading>
  <text>No person or organization shall sell, transfer or otherwise dispose of any firearm, destructive device or ammunition in the District except as provided in <cite path="§7-2502.10|(c)">§ 7-2502.10(c)</cite>, <cite path="§7-2505.02">§ 7-2505.02</cite>, <cite path="§7-2507.05">§ 7-2507.05</cite>, <cite path="§7-2510.07">§ 7-2510.07</cite>, or <cite path="§7-2510.09">§ 7-2510.09</cite>.</text>
